A medieval walled city at dusk rendered in Studio Ghibli style, featuring concentric stone walls with multiple defensive layers, a deep moat with still water reflecting amber sunset light, and watchtowers with glowing lanterns positioned at strategic points. Tiny armored guards patrol the ramparts while carrier pigeons fly between towers. Outside the walls, shadowy formless shapes lurk in a misty forest, unable to penetrate the defenses. Inside the innermost wall, warm light spills from cottage windows where villagers go about their peaceful evening routines, completely protected. The color palette blends soft oranges, deep blues, and warm yellows, with detailed hand-painted textures on stone and foliage characteristic of Japanese animation.
